{"tid":568066,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個要用腦，破壞友情嘅board game","createTime":"2018-02-21T12:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T20:35:56.000Z","uid":158055,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a2bc2f3dd201d0330549b33adfa171326f4716","tid":568066,"uid":158055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T12:22:05.000Z","msg":"1.狼人/ killer, 依個唔洗講，中學玩到u都仲玩緊<br />\n<br />\n2.stop the bus,啤牌驚，一人三隻牌，jqk功能牌，7係0，輪住抽牌，換手牌，最後鬥細，有趣在你唔會知你一開始果三隻係咩牌，有可能3條7就咁換曬出去<br />\n<br />\n3.uno,+2+4，驚嬲女仔嘅最佳選擇<br />\n<br />\n仲有兩種唔記得咩名<br />\n有一種係有三種卡，角色，武器，地點，跟住要最快搵到邊個人係邊死同死<br />\n另一種，有啲似狼人，投票估邊個係兇手，好考人緣<br />\n<br />\n好中意玩果啲推理game<br />\n各位仲有冇玩過啲咩正嘅boardgame?<br />\n賭錢果啲就不了"},{"pid":"20403e3e39feb5ef35e0b80d8ccce28cbef596e6","tid":568066,"uid":104171,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"掘金"},{"pid":"c9c8dc250be3ce411f890a2007a64e010f4c60b2","tid":568066,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T12:38:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ce1a07312b9a6124d4bcfd0771be2599095839e","tid":568066,"uid":144001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"Risk 戰國風雲"},{"pid":"9271ed8178660d7ba7752e8726f9a72f4c666a25","tid":568066,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"小朋友落樓梯"},{"pid":"c6eacce92d47f601682cd41fde1d156654bdac7a","tid":568066,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"係咪你冇朋友渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d605c509eef6176969e7fb60be5da271b5cb1e02","tid":568066,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"TTA<br />\nSeasons"},{"pid":"29e74f3f967334a8180dd3a4f906fa7d26d36561","tid":568066,"uid":59465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"原